_header: When Phoebus passed was the Ram
_description: Fragment beginning of a Humphrey Newton poem — four lines in couplets

BodLatMisC66.Transcription:
Quene phebus passyd was þe ramand in myd april into þe bull
                    cameand saturnus with ys frosty faceIn Iubiter had takyn hym a
                    place…
